data.description: What a wonderful place to call home!  If you long for space then look no further!  This beauty has 4 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms!  The family will love the spacious kitchen and living room with a fireplace.  The impressive dining room will serve the family and friends.  Upstairs there is an office, den and 4th bedroom plus a nice bathroom.  The space in this home could be used in many ways so you get to choose!!  The back yard is large and there is a covered beautiful back patio porch.
